Name: Pandum online
About the game: Pandum is a 3D crossplatform (android/windows/linux) MMORPG with an arcadified gameplay. In game party voice message In game custom avatar can be uploaded from web site Arena team battle with ranking (see web site) PVP everywhere (except trade zone and dungeon instances) Free character skill path Free to play and free to win (shop doesn't provide items unbalancing combat)
